Encoders Notes
I dropped the source into vdubmod.
I lowered the brightness, increased the contrast & gamma.
Then i spent a while changing the colors with a rgb eq.
Finaly i sharpened it.
Its not a bad TS.
The colours were prety bad, i tried my best but in parts
it was to yellow & in other parts it was to purple.
Its dark in places but that was the only way to remove the yellow-ish tint.
